{#-
  Auth-MagicLink — terminal passwordless-login confirmation (Ring 3 S3.1b).

  Structural twin of Auth-EmailVerification — same shell + Empty + Resend
  composition, different microcopy + flow (passwordless login vs sign-up).

  Composes `_auth-shell` (title null) + Empty (lg, h1, icon=check
  substitut — see Auth-EmailVerification §1 Doctrine for the curated-set
  rationale) + Button × 1-2.

  Pure server-rendered terminal page (OQ-55). 0 Stimulus controller.
  Typical entry point : passwordless login flow (user enters email at
  /login → consumer's auth back-end emails a one-time sign-in link →
  redirects user here).

  Microcopy : body explicitly states the `{expirationMinutes}`
  constraint ("Lien valable {expirationMinutes} minutes."). Consumer
  interpolates the value via t() params — default 15 min, consumer
  chooses per their security policy.

  See `docs/specs/ring3/Auth-MagicLink.md` for the full spec.
-#}

{%- set title             = title             | default('theme.auth.magic-link.title'|trans) -%}
{%- set body              = body              | default('theme.auth.magic-link.body'|trans({'{expirationMinutes}': 15})) -%}
{%- set resendLabel       = resendLabel       | default('theme.auth.magic-link.resend-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set resendHref        = resendHref        | default('#') -%}
{%- set backToLoginLabel  = backToLoginLabel  | default('theme.auth.magic-link.back-to-login-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set backToLoginHref   = backToLoginHref   | default(null) -%}
{%- set htmlId            = htmlId            | default('cremona-auth-magic-link') -%}
{%- set className         = className         | default('') -%}

{% embed '@cremona/components/_auth-shell/_auth-shell.html.twig' with {
  title: null,
  htmlId: htmlId,
  variant: 'default',
  className: ('cremona-auth-magic-link ' ~ className)|trim,
} %}
  {% block content %}
    {% embed '@cremona/components/empty/empty.html.twig' with {
      title: title,
      body: body,
      icon: 'check',
      size: 'lg',
      titleLevel: 'h1',
      htmlId: htmlId ~ '-empty',
    } %}
      {% block actions %}
        {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
          label: resendLabel,
          variant: 'secondary',
          size: 'md',
          href: resendHref,
        } %}
        {% if backToLoginHref %}
          {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
            label: backToLoginLabel,
            variant: 'ghost',
            size: 'md',
            href: backToLoginHref,
            iconLeading: 'arrow-left',
          } %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endblock %}
    {% endembed %}
  {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
